{"tid":692020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"facebook再有洩漏 承認與中資企業分享用戶資料","createTime":"2018-06-06T09:03:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T21:29:12.000Z","uid":1251,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"04a3a74de593ff75b5050b5409c9f1612131692d","tid":692020,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T09:03:40.000Z","msg":"facebook 承認，跟最少四間中資企業分享用戶資料，包括被指與中國政府關係密切的電訊設備製造商華為。<br />\n<br />\n《紐約時報》報道， facebook 與華為、聯想、歐珀及 TCL 通訊四間公司協議，所分享的資料包括用戶工作和教育背景、與伴侶的關係、以及所點擊喜愛的題目等。<br />\n<br />\nfacebook 強調，用戶資料只會儲存在手機產品，而非相關公司的伺服器上。<br />\n<br />\nfacebook 與另外數十間企業，包括蘋果、三星、 HTC 等，亦有類似協議。<br />\n<br />\n#有線新聞　#Facebook　#洩漏　#用戶資料　#華為　#聯想　#歐珀　#TCL通訊"},{"pid":"8c4a46cb1c6904c8f88486fdb104ba7e8f967ce7","tid":692020,"uid":177047,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T14:05:19.000Z","msg":"朱西賤格真係為左打入支那14億人市場而好比心機投共,真係做好多野<br />\n不過刁種唔撚睬佢,仲係'養唔熟'<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e48b3036f4d97a1816061dbc2c84cef4ee96ebfa","tid":692020,"uid":53705,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"8c4a46cb1c6904c8f88486fdb104ba7e8f967ce7","tid":692020,"uid":177047,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T14:05:19.000Z","msg":"朱西賤格真係為左打入支那14億人市場而好比心機投共,真係做好多野<br />\n不過刁種唔撚睬佢,仲係'養唔熟'<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T14:15:59.000Z","msg":"完全唔明白<br />\n條友已經咁有錢, D錢十世都用唔完, 點解為左奶共, 連尊嚴都唔要?"},{"pid":"0bbe8ec4f70dce88e2fbac8343eacd7846e62a6b","tid":692020,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T14:18:55.000Z","msg":"用個人資料玩fb已經係on99啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"517ee7041e71a2ae43dd117319119e3d1cd8fdc6","tid":692020,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e48b3036f4d97a1816061dbc2c84cef4ee96ebfa","tid":692020,"uid":53705,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"8c4a46cb1c6904c8f88486fd